data.name: XCompoundTypeDescription
desc: For struct types, this type is superseded by XStructTypeDescription, which supports polymorphic struct types.

methods.name: getBaseType
desc: Returns the type of the base type of the compound type.
If the compound does not have a base type, the method returns a null interface.

methods.name: getMemberNames
desc: Returns the member names of the struct/exception in IDL declaration order.

methods.name: getMemberTypes
desc: Returns the member types of the struct/exception in IDL declaration order.

For a polymorphic struct type template, a member of parameterized type is represented by an instance of com.sun.star.reflection.XTypeDescription whose type class is UNKNOWN and whose name is the name of the type parameter.
